<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Ticket Booking</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #4CAF50;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Your Ticket is Booked!</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= data.name %>,</p>
    <p>We are pleased to inform you that your ticket for the event <span class="highlight"><%= data.eventName %></span> has been successfully booked.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing us. We look forward to seeing you at the event!</p>
    
    <p class="footer">
      Best regards,<br>Event Team
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
